# SARA: Adaptive Retrieval and Context Compression Framework

[![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.8+-blue.svg)](https://www.python.org/downloads/)
[![PyTorch](https://img.shields.io/badge/PyTorch-2.0+-red.svg)](https://pytorch.org/)

SARA is a comprehensive framework for adaptive retrieval and context compression in question-answering systems. It provides unified interfaces for evidence selection, compression, and QA model integration with clear parameter specifications and modular architecture.

