The refactored pipeline has been thoroughly tested to ensure:
- ✅ All components initialize correctly
- ✅ Evidence allocation works as expected  
- ✅ QA model inputs are generated properly
- ✅ Backward compatibility is maintained
- ✅ Error handling works correctly

All tests pass successfully:
